{
  "texts": [
    "Channel feature attention layerIn light of Residual's robust feature extraction capabilities within the spatial domain, an attention mechanism known as \"squeeze-and-excitation blocks,\" was incorporated into the feature channel domain.",
    "This attention mechanism operates by modifying the weights of distinct feature maps within the channel domain to selectively choose significant features.",
    "In order to leverage the channel attention module to its full potential without introducing a large number of parameters, the channel attention mechanism is exclusively applied to the dense block and transition layers.",
    "Additionally, the channel attention network is designed to be compact and efficient, contributing only 0.22M parameters and posing no risk of overfitting.",
    "The transition layer comprises a 1 x 1 convolution layer and an average pooling operation with a stride of 2 that works to decrease the size of the feature map."
  ]
}